de.oaam.model.oaam.systems

Interface Information

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ModeDependentElementA, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OaamBaseElementA, ProvidedOutputA, RequiredInputA, VariantDependentElementA

    public interface Information
extends ProvidedOutputA, RequiredInputA, OaamBaseElementA, ModeDependentElementA, VariantDependentElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Information'. An information is an abstract definition of any kind of data flow between systems.

    The following features are supported:

    • Rate
    • Latency
    • Accuracy
    • Resolution
    • Unit
    See Also:
    de.oaam.model.oaam.systems.SystemsPackage#getInformation()
